### 1. Login as Admin to get token
POST http://localhost:5166/api/Account/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@lessonplan.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### 2. Get all accounts (Admin only) - Copy token from step 1
GET http://localhost:5166/api/Account
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 3. Get all accounts with pagination
GET http://localhost:5166/api/Account?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 4. Get all accounts grouped by role
GET http://localhost:5166/api/Account/all
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Delete account by ID (Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:5166/api/Account/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

